{"msg":{"practice":[{"id":148,"question":"假设你是某公司经理，你的下属在给你的报告中有很多错别字，下边对他的批评哪一个是恰当的？","type":1,"analysis":"这道题比较有迷惑性的是A项。A虽然语气还算不错，但是他把某一具体行为升级成了对整个人的评价。好的批评是对事不对人的，不要轻易给他人贴标签","pic":null,"difficulty":3,"knowledgeId":12,"sceneId":1,"del":false,"problemId":5,"sequence":4,"example":false,"practiceUid":"TT005B005B001X01004","score":50,"choiceList":[{"id":437,"questionId":148,"subject":"哎呀，你可真是个粗心的人，拿回去把错别字都改掉再给我","sequence":1,"isRight":false,"selected":false},{"id":438,"questionId":148,"subject":"简直蠢死了！拿去重写！","sequence":2,"isRight":false,"selected":false},{"id":439,"questionId":148,"subject":"这篇报告错别字太多了，拿回去改掉","sequence":3,"isRight":true,"selected":false}],"discussList":[{"id":1684,"warmupPracticeId":148,"repliedId":null,"comment":"不过AB真的是职场上最常见的现象。","openid":null,"addTime":1491114348000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":null,"del":0,"repliedName":null,"name":"kerry","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay5cUlGv2ibxydlESCOjsMG6yNquicDV2grtRHY4e6BREibMTu7aYqiaYHGMSVmVfneOdxIhRkLicP5at1/0","discussTime":"2017-04-02"},{"id":820,"warmupPracticeId":148,"repliedId":null,"comment":"送分题","openid":null,"addTime":1489311530000,"priority":0,"repliedOpenid":null,"repliedComment":null,"del":0,"repliedName":null,"name":"零五七","avatar":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcLrFd5bPVEw4BRmkPkP5sMhsygdDwvgHiaWISQXnIXqBeHRX9uOIiciaRwETN4FxUeO0ktPBBBORFgmC37DFAUkJd0/0","discussTime":"2017-03-12"}],"choice":null,"knowledge":{"id":12,"knowledge":"人身攻击谬误","step":"识别谬误：低难度","analysis":"接触观点时，扫除“对人不对事”的思维误区，防止被误导；\n与人辩论时，识破对方的人身攻击谬误，避免陷入口水战。","means":"在论证过程中，为了降低对方可信度或加强自身可信度，常常陷入以下两种逻辑谬误：\n\n1）直接人身攻击：对他人直接指责或评判，并以此为论据，质疑他人的推论或主张的质量。\n2）隐藏的人身攻击：恶意询问对方在某件隐私事情上的具体行为。\n","keynote":"1）遇到人身攻击时，关键是要保持冷静，不要自乱阵脚\n2）必要时可以考虑终止讨论","pic":null,"audio":"http://www.iqycamp.com/audio/rise_k12.m4a","appear":0,"example":null}}]},"code":200}
